Titolo: Sundered

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Sundered is a metroidvania video game developed and published by Canadian studio Thunder Lotus Games. It was released on July 28, 2017 for Windows, Mac OS, Linux, and PlayStation 4. A definitive version of the game, Sundered: Eldritch Edition, was released on December 21, 2018 for Nintendo Switch and Xbox One and on May 26, 2020 on Stadia.

Genere: Roguelike

Valutazione: 72
